## General info

Display the work orders in lastest/ earlist deadline and view the worker for each work order.
User can search the work order base on the name of the worker.

## Technologies

Project is created with:

- Next.js

## Setup

To run this project, install it locally using npm:

```
$ cd ../work-orders
& npm install
$ npm run dev / next dev
```
